core

Class Snake

  • java.lang.Object
    • core.Snake

  • public class Snake
extends java.lang.Object
    A Snake is made up of one or more SnakeSegment. The first SnakeSegment is the "head" of the snake. The last SnakeSegment is the "tail" of the snake. As the snake moves, it adds one cell to the head and then removes one from the tail. If the snake eats a piece of food, the head adds one cell but the tail will not shrink.
